== Welcome to Lighthouse Burndown Beacon

Looks at lighthouse tickets from nominated project closed since last download. Summarises daily activity and stores for determining velocity or any other analisys at your leisure. In order to utilise thise, place a point:x tag against each ticket (where x is number of points you want to assign to the ticket. e.g points:3.5 points :7 etc).

To get started edit lib/burndown_lighthouse.rb and configure token, account and @@project_id to your situation.
